	Three modes ->	insert -------> command --------> visual 

insert mode ðŸ’­ï¸

	i	=>	insert mode

command modeðŸ’­ï¸
	:q	=> quit (not save)
	:wq	=> save and quit
	:q!	=> force quit (not save)

visual modeðŸ’­ï¸
	v       =>	visual
	ctrl+v  =>	visual block
	shift+v =>	visual line	

	y 	=>	yank (copy)
	p	=>	paste (to paste go to command mode first)

